headline.print_headline: Ajax Leave It Late to Polish Off Struggling Excelsior
headline.main: Ajax Leave It Late to Polish Off Struggling Excelsior

lead_paragraph: - Ajax Amsterdam, still smarting from a shock 4-0 Dutch Cup thrashing by Vitesse Arnhem on Thursday, left it late before finally easing past struggling Excelsior 2-0 in the league on Sunday.
